    <p>The Gal­lop Barn Stay Ex­pe­ri­ence at Gal­lop Hill Top Re­sort in Horsecity in Bukit Timah al­lows guests to get up close with horses.</p>
    <p>The deal for two in­cludes a 60-minute ses­sion at the Gal­lop Sta­ble, where you can feed the equine oc­cu­pants; a pony or horse ride; and a farm­house break­fast ex­pe­ri­ence with horses by the pad­dock on the ho­tel’s lawn.</p>
    <p>The sta­ble ex­pe­ri­ence and horse rides are lim­ited to ages three to 55, and rid­ers must weigh 75kg or less. Rates: From $348++ a room a night. Pay an ex­tra $100 a child. Stay by Jan 9 next year. Info: Call 6463-6012 or e-mail en­quiry@ gal­lop­stable. com</p>


